snippet.title: Welcome To Go Play - Kids Indoor Play & Café Pretoria
snippet.description:
Go-Play offers three play areas, as well as an additional activity area for children to have hours of fun. Adults can relax in our Cafeteria Area enjoying free Wi-Fi, big screen TV’s and a very comprehensive menu whilst viewing their children happy at play.

The one play area accommodates from babies to 4 year olds and the second area accommodates children between the ages of 4 and 10. The Centre provides a well ventilated, safe environment for children between the ages of 0 and 10 to enjoy hours of fun. At Go-Play we are dedicated to child physical and mental improvement, and have therefore structured challenges to improve gross and fine motor skills, hand-eye coordination and spatial awareness.

The indoor Centre is fully-equipped with industry approved and hygienic child-friendly equipment including slides, soft play obstacles and mazes. At Go-Play we take safety seriously, and therefore conduct regular inspections of each piece of equipment and place trained child minders on each level at each station – allowing parents peace of mind

The Outside area offers a track where children can enjoy hours of fun riding plastic scooters, while the parents relax enjoying a spectacular view of the Golf course and Lake

Visit our website at http://go-play.co.za
